Somnolence-Detector
===================

This product includes software developed by third parties:

1. Ultralytics YOLO11
   https://github.com/ultralytics/ultralytics
   Licensed under AGPL-3.0-or-later.
   Pre-trained YOLO11n weights (COCO) are used for cell-phone object
   detection. The weights themselves are distributed by Ultralytics
   under the same AGPL-3.0 license.

2. Tencent NCNN
   https://github.com/Tencent/ncnn
   Licensed under BSD-3-Clause.
   Used as the inference runtime on Raspberry Pi for the YOLO model
   exported via `scripts/export_yolo_ncnn.py`.

3. Google MediaPipe
   https://github.com/google/mediapipe
   Licensed under Apache-2.0.
   Used for face-mesh and hand landmark tracking in the edge detector.

4. OpenCV
   https://github.com/opencv/opencv
   Licensed under Apache-2.0.

Because this project links against AGPL-3.0 code (Ultralytics), the
combined source is distributed under AGPL-3.0-or-later. Any derivative
that offers this system as a network-accessible service must publish
